This was actually a miscalculation on my part. I thought I could win a pawn by taking d4 with my bishop but I overlooked the fact that after Qxd4 there would be a mate threat on g7. Still though I'm not certain that this exchange is too bad, it does give white a good centre however I'm not sure what my other options would have been. Maybe Bg7.
